Saying that. Grouping with Lightbringers for others. IT depends on what kind of evil you are playing. Shintou is a Fanatic. Hard lined and into advancing evil by only evil ways, also the pride of being evil (or dark as I am learning to call it when RPing), and having pride in that strenght.<br>
